  "messages": [
   {
    "with": "Source 'Aral'",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Following up on the documents you sent last week. Can you confirm the shell company's registration date?",
    "time": "2026-05-04T11:22:49"
   },
   {
    "with": "Temur",
    "direction": "from",
    "text": "Just got word from a source that the minister's team is looking into our outlet's funding. Be careful with your next piece.",
    "time": "2026-05-05T12:33:00"
   },
   {
    "with": "Madina",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Hey, cuz. Just checking in. How's life in Berlin? Any news on the visa front?",
    "time": "2026-05-06T11:49:54"
   },
   {
    "with": "Yerlan",
    "direction": "from",
    "text": "Sis, mom's doing okay. Just had a check-up and the doctor says she's stable. But we need to talk about your articles... they're causing trouble for me at work.",
    "time": "2026-05-07T12:27:31"
   },
   {
    "with": "Source 'Aral'",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "I've reviewed the new documents. The transaction patterns match what I suspected. Can you get me more on the beneficial owners?",
    "time": "2026-05-08T11:01:58"
   },
   {
    "with": "Temur",
    "direction": "from",
    "text": "We need to discuss the latest draft. I've got some notes and we should finalize the piece ASAP before things escalate further.",
    "time": "2026-05-09T12:25:38"
   },
   {
    "with": "Madina",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Just had a weird feeling someone was watching me at the café today. Probably just paranoia, but keep an ear out for anything unusual, okay?",
    "time": "2026-05-10T11:46:20"
   },
   {
    "with": "Mother",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Привет, мама, как ты? Не забудь закрыть окна, на улице холодно",
    "time": "2026-05-11T09:47:49"
   },
   {
    "with": "Madina",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Прогресс в расследовании министра. Нашла интересные документы, нужно обсудить",
    "time": "2026-05-11T20:08:00"
   },
   {
    "with": "Mother",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Мама, я беспокоюсь о твоем здоровье. Ты сходила к врачу в этом месяце?",
    "time": "2026-05-12T15:34:54"
   },
   {
    "with": "Temur",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Темур, нужно обсудить статью о министре. Есть новые факты, которые могут все изменить",
    "time": "2026-05-13T11:52:31"
   },
   {
    "with": "Aral",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Арал, спасибо за последние документы. Они очень важны для расследования. Можно ли ожидать новых материалов?",
    "time": "2026-05-13T20:01:58"
   },
   {
    "with": "Mother",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Мама, не волнуйся, я все под контролем. Просто занята работой",
    "time": "2026-05-14T15:30:38"
   },
   {
    "with": "Temur",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Темур, статья готова. Можно ли согласовать окончательный вариант?",
    "time": "2026-05-15T11:36:20"
   },
   {
    "with": "Madina",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Мадина, расследование почти закончено. Нужно обсудить последние детали",
    "time": "2026-05-16T15:22:14"
   },
   {
    "with": "Mother",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Привет, мама, как твое настроение? Мне не хватает тебя",
    "time": "2026-05-17T11:30:09"
   },
   {
    "with": "Source 'Aral'",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Need confirmation on the minister's nominee structures. Can you provide more documents?",
    "time": "2026-05-18T11:12:49"
   },
   {
    "with": "Madina K.",
    "direction": "from",
    "text": "Be careful, I heard rumors of surveillance on our people in Tbilisi. Maybe we should meet in person soon?",
    "time": "2026-05-18T22:33:00"
   },
   {
    "with": "Unknown",
    "direction": "from",
    "text": "You're being watched. Drop the investigation.",
    "time": "2026-05-19T21:24:54"
   },
   {
    "with": "Yerlan",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "How's Aigerim and Dana? I feel so far away from everything. Missing you all.",
    "time": "2026-05-20T19:17:31"
   },
   {
    "with": "Madina K.",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "I've hit a wall with the minister's assets. Any ideas on how to proceed without blowing my cover?",
    "time": "2026-05-21T20:41:58"
   },
   {
    "with": "Unknown",
    "direction": "from",
    "text": "Your mother is not safe. Back off the story.",
    "time": "2026-05-22T19:35:38"
   },
   {
    "with": "Yerlan",
    "direction": "from",
    "text": "Dana is asking about you. When can we visit? Be careful, sis.",
    "time": "2026-05-23T21:16:20"
   },
   {
    "with": "Madina K.",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "I'm getting close to something big. If anything happens to me, make sure Temur gets the story out.",
    "time": "2026-05-24T19:22:14"
   },
   {
    "with": "Source 'Aral'",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Confirming meeting details for the document handover. Please confirm your availability.",
    "time": "2026-05-25T11:17:49"
   },
   {
    "with": "Madina K.",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Need to discuss the latest findings on the minister's offshore assets. Can we schedule a call today?",
    "time": "2026-05-26T12:23:00"
   },
   {
    "with": "Temur",
    "direction": "from",
    "text": "Investigation update: we've received new information that requires your immediate attention. Let's discuss during our meeting tomorrow.",
    "time": "2026-05-27T11:44:54"
   },
   {
    "with": "Source 'Aral'",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Reconfirming the meeting location and time. Please acknowledge receipt of this message.",
    "time": "2026-05-28T12:27:31"
   },
   {
    "with": "Madina K.",
    "direction": "from",
    "text": "Received your message. The investigation is progressing, but we need to be cautious. Let's discuss the details over a secure channel.",
    "time": "2026-05-29T11:51:58"
   },
   {
    "with": "Temur",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Updating you on the investigation's progress. We have new leads that require your review and input.",
    "time": "2026-05-30T12:55:38"
   },
   {
    "with": "Source 'Aral'",
    "direction": "from",
    "text": "Meeting details confirmed. I will provide the documents as agreed. Be cautious and watch for surveillance.",
    "time": "2026-05-31T11:26:20"
   },
   {
    "with": "Source 'Aral'",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Need more docs on minister's nominee structures, specifically SWIFT memos from 2022. Can you provide?",
    "time": "2026-06-01T11:12:49"
   },
   {
    "with": "Madina K.",
    "direction": "from",
    "text": "Heard rumors of a second whistleblower in Astana. Might be worth exploring. Will discuss in our next call.",
    "time": "2026-06-01T18:03:00"
   },
   {
    "with": "Yerlan",
    "direction": "to",
    "text": "Hey, brother. Just checking in. How's Aigerim and Dana? And how's work? Be careful what you say over this line.",
    "time": "2026-06-02T11:44:54"
   },
   {
    "with": "Unknown",
    "direction": "from",
    "text": "You're playing with fire, 'astrakhan_owl'. Back off the minister story, or we'll make sure your mother's 'health' becomes a concern. You know what we can do.",
    "time": "2026-06-02T20:07:31"
   }
